Use 6811 Downloader to download pcode_hb.s19.  Power cycle, and the
Handy Board should beep and display a version message on its LCD
screen.

Then, run IC modem or IC printer depending on which port you are
using.  It should be configured to boot with lib_hb.lis.

Fred

